data.title: Raquel Torres married to Stephen
data.meta_description:
Raquel Torres married to Stephen Ames aboard a liner ._x000D_
Raquel Torres , the Mexican screen actress , and Stephen Ames , former husband of Adrienne Ames , were married aboard the liner Lurline in Los Angeles harbour . After the ceremony the couple sailed aboard the same ship for a honeymoon in Honolulu ._x000D_
Photo shows , Raquel Torres and Stephen Ames after their wedding . _x000D_
2 May 1934

Raquel Torres married to Stephen Ames aboard a liner ._x000D_

Raquel Torres , the Mexican screen actress , and Stephen Ames , former husband of Adrienne Ames , were married aboard the liner Lurline in Los Angeles harbour . After the ceremony the couple sailed aboard the same ship for a honeymoon in Honolulu ._x000D_
